tted spectra when, as often the case, it is effective\nat optical depths tau ~ 1. The emergent spectrum is independent of the\nparameters of the convection model.(Abstract shortened)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Sep 2008 16:10:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 22 Jun 2010 21:52:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-13"}
